Fox anchor Harris Faulkner is joining the chorus of Fox figures suggesting perhaps the coronavirus death toll is over-inflated 

Fox anchor: "How many of those people had other risks at play and maybe, in fact, it wasn't COVID-19 that caused their death." https://t.co/7Cs1K4ryeT
